gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 93, Spurs 82
gameRecap.excerpt: The Rockets defeated the Spurs, 93-82. Tari Eason recorded 18 points (14 in the 4th quarter) and a career-high 14 rebounds for the Rockets, while Fred VanVleet added 16 points, six rebounds and five assists in the victory. Victor Wembanyama tallied 15 points, 18 rebounds and 5 blocks for the Spurs in the losing effort. The Rockets improve to 11-9 on the season, while the Spurs fall to 3-19.
